1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:03,710
(Episode 90)

2
00:00:10,050 --> 00:00:11,980
The person you called is unavailable.

3
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,330
Baek Ho, I'm so sorry.

4
00:00:27,930 --> 00:00:29,770
I'm sorry for making you go home
by yourself,

5
00:00:31,100 --> 00:00:32,670
and I'm sorry for leaving you all alone.

6
00:00:36,070 --> 00:00:37,940
I'll take on all the pain
for the both of us.

7
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:41,550
I just want you to be safe...

8
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:43,750
and stay in the light.

9
00:00:46,020 --> 00:00:47,020
I love you,

10
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:49,450
Baek Ho.

11
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,600
Tae Pyung.

12
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:01,870
I can't get a hold of Jang Mi.

13
00:01:02,070 --> 00:01:03,170
Jang Mi...

14
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,000
Jang Mi...

15
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,770
You knew about this, didn't you?

16
00:01:10,740 --> 00:01:14,850
- Baek Ho, let's talk about this outside.
- I'm asking you if you knew!

17
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:17,080
Tae Pyung.

18
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:20,220
You should have stopped her.

19
00:01:20,790 --> 00:01:23,250
She's trying to handle everything
on her own.

20
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:27,790
I think she's doing this because of me.
You should've stopped her!

21
00:01:27,890 --> 00:01:31,200
Baek Ho.
Just calm down for a second, okay?

22
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:39,940
(Oh Bok Gil)

23
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:41,410
Dad.

24
00:01:42,540 --> 00:01:43,810
I did the right thing, didn't I?

25
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,410
I couldn't even protect you,

26
00:01:48,250 --> 00:01:49,610
and I couldn't protect Mom either.

27
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:52,980
And now I've even gotten Baek Ho hurt.

28
00:01:54,450 --> 00:01:55,920
What right do I have...

29
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,560
to be with someone so wonderful?

30
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,390
I have to go through this torment alone.

31
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:04,200
Right, Dad?

32
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:07,870
I did the right thing, didn't I?

33
00:02:15,210 --> 00:02:16,340
Was I...

34
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:19,740
a burden to her?

35
00:02:20,010 --> 00:02:22,610
- That's not it, Baek Ho.
- It's because I got hurt.

36
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:26,080
I didn't even think about
how she must have felt,

37
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:28,690
and I just kept digging into the past.

38
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:32,290
I guess that's why she did it.

39
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:36,360
I feel so terrible. What am I going to do?

40
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:38,760
It couldn't have been an easy decision
for Jang Mi.

41
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,800
Please, just try to understand that.

42
00:02:47,970 --> 00:02:48,970
Kang Baek Ho.

43
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:52,340
I can't stand to see you suffer
like this anymore.

44
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:56,480
This is the only thing I can do for you.

45
00:02:57,850 --> 00:03:00,790
Tae Pyung, I'm going to go see Dad.

46
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:03,090
I want to be alone right now.

47
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,760
Thanks, Tae Pyung. Thank you.

48
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:26,910
Get up.

49
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,680
Did you call me here just to show me
how miserable you were?

50
00:03:30,650 --> 00:03:32,720
Did you want to show me
how hard it was for you...

51
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:34,420
to break up with Baek Ho?

52
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:38,220
In case Baek Ho comes looking for me,

53
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,630
I wanted him to see me with you.

54
00:03:42,790 --> 00:03:44,300
So you're going to use me.

55
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,270
Yes, that's right. I am.

56
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:50,370
Fine.

57
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:52,970
Use me all you want.

58
00:03:55,010 --> 00:03:56,010
Let's go.

59
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,180
How...

60
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,920
What are you doing here?

61
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:15,090
I came to pay my respects to her father
before our wedding.

62
00:04:16,030 --> 00:04:17,900
- Wedding?
- I'm...

63
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,960
marrying Jun Ho.

64
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:23,270
What did you say?

65
00:04:23,570 --> 00:04:24,640
That's right.

66
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:27,440
Oh Jang Mi is my woman now.

67
00:04:27,770 --> 00:04:28,810
No, Jun Ho...

68
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:33,040
You know she's Jang Mi and not Seo Rin?

69
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:34,250
I told him.

70
00:04:35,410 --> 00:04:37,720
I told him that I was actually...

71
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:40,520
Oh Jang Mi, just pretending to be Seo Rin.

72
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:43,550
Jang Mi, this is ridiculous.

73
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:47,090
Why would you suddenly decide to marry
my brother?

74
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:49,260
- That's enough, Baek Ho.
- Stay out of this, Jun Ho.

75
00:04:49,590 --> 00:04:51,130
I'm talking to Jang Mi right now.

76
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:56,630
Jang Mi, make me understand.

77
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,440
I just can't wrap my head around this.

78
00:04:58,700 --> 00:05:00,140
But you love me.

79
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,570
Is this because I got hurt?

80
00:05:03,780 --> 00:05:06,010
You had nothing to do with my brother.
So why are you suddenly...

81
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,810
marrying my brother of all people?

82
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,080
That's it!

83
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,480
Didn't I tell you to stop?

84
00:05:13,650 --> 00:05:14,650
Hey, Kang Baek Ho.

85
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,490
Did you not hear what I just said?

86
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,190
Oh Jang Mi is my woman now.

87
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:23,460
I'm not going to say this again,
so listen up.

88
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,560
Don't you ever go near Jang Mi again.

89
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:28,800
She's going to be your sister-in-law.

90
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:38,210
I'm completely lost.

91
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,050
I have no idea what's going on.

92
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,220
I just don't get it.

93
00:05:46,050 --> 00:05:48,120
I already told you, Baek Ho.

94
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:50,350
That I...

95
00:05:50,890 --> 00:05:53,020
want to live my life as Ma Seo Rin.

96
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,190
And...

97
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:57,600
And...

98
00:05:58,930 --> 00:06:00,160
I'm in love with Jun Ho.

99
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,100
That's ridiculous.

100
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:04,640
Don't lie to me, please!

101
00:06:07,670 --> 00:06:09,970
- I don't believe you.
- I already told you, Baek Ho.

102
00:06:11,010 --> 00:06:13,780
I told you I've liked Jun Ho
since he was a chef.

103
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,150
Is that a good enough answer for you?

104
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:18,320
You can't even look me in the eye
right now.

105
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:20,620
And you expect me to believe you?

106
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:22,620
I know it's hard to understand right now,

107
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,890
but you'll be okay in time.

108
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,460
Let's go, Jun Ho.

109
00:06:39,770 --> 00:06:41,070
Wait, Jang Mi.

110
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:42,340
Wait!

111
00:06:43,710 --> 00:06:45,480
You didn't have to hit him.

112
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,280
He has just gotten out of the hospital.

113
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:51,480
You clearly still have feelings for him.

114
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,550
Jang Mi!

115
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:55,250
Jang Mi!

116
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:03,230
Let me just talk to him for a second.

117
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,230
Alright.

118
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,740
I don't know what I did wrong,

119
00:07:16,010 --> 00:07:17,010
but I'm sorry.

120
00:07:17,980 --> 00:07:19,040
I'm really sorry.

121
00:07:20,410 --> 00:07:22,010
It's all my fault.

122
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:24,820
So please...

123
00:07:26,150 --> 00:07:27,290
Please don't do this.

124
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:29,890
I'm not Oh Jang Mi anymore.

125
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:32,060
No...

126
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,730
I'm not the Oh Jang Mi
who's just imitating Ma Seo Rin.

127
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:37,630
I've decided to truly live as Ma Seo Rin.

128
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:40,000
Not a fake, but the real deal.

129
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:44,040
I will live as Ma Seo Rin.

130
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:46,170
Nothing will change my mind.

131
00:07:46,470 --> 00:07:48,470
Jang Mi, please don't be like this.

132
00:07:49,170 --> 00:07:50,510
This isn't like you.
Why are you acting this way?

133
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:52,210
I've chosen to live Ma Seo Rin's life.

134
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:54,580
So don't try to sway me.

135
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,620
That's the greatest thing
you can do for me...

136
00:07:58,450 --> 00:07:59,520
as a final gift.

137
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,090
Jang Mi,

138
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:03,720
you can never become Ma Seo Rin.

139
00:08:05,290 --> 00:08:07,090
Are you saying you'll never see
your mother again?

140
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:09,660
Are you just going to abandon
your entire family?

141
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,960
You know you can't do that.

142
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:14,770
You're someone who sacrificed everything
for her family.

143
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,930
Yes, I was!

144
00:08:16,670 --> 00:08:18,340
But I'm completely sick and tired
of it now.

145
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:21,410
You, of all people, know how I've lived.

146
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:25,240
You know how much I suffered
because of my mom and family!

147
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:30,210
So I'm throwing all that away
to live for my own happiness.

148
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:32,650
And what's so wrong with that?

149
00:08:32,650 --> 00:08:34,150
If you throw everything away,

150
00:08:34,690 --> 00:08:37,590
do you really think you can be happy
living as someone else?

151
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:40,220
If that can really make you happy...

152
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,290
If it honestly can,

153
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,330
I'll let you go without another word.

154
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,700
But I know you better than that, Jang Mi.

155
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:48,830
You're not the kind of person
who could ever be happy like that.

156
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:51,170
What makes you think you know me so well,
Baek Ho?

157
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,740
Please...

158
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:55,140
stop pretending you know
what I'm going through.

159
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:57,210
Don't cross the line.

160
00:08:57,780 --> 00:08:59,410
Don't do this, Jang Mi.

161
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:01,750
You said you wanted to get back
at CEO Chae,

162
00:09:02,050 --> 00:09:03,550
so why are you teaming up with my brother?

163
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:05,520
This is just wrong.

164
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:06,750
Stop it.

165
00:09:07,420 --> 00:09:08,420
Enough.

166
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:11,660
Let me make you happy.

167
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:14,560
We're all we need.

168
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:16,490
Right?

169
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,470
I can no longer be happy...

170
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:27,410
being with you anymore.

171
00:09:28,810 --> 00:09:29,940
I've said what I have to say.

172
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:37,550
Jang Mi.

173
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:48,930
Excuse me. This man is mine.

174
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:30,800
(Hall of Love)

175
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:46,020
(Hall of Love)

176
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:47,890
Jang Mi!

177
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,290
This is crazy! Jang Mi!

178
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:51,020
Jang Mi!

179
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,320
Jang Mi!

180
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:25,590
I hope the food is to your liking.

181
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,960
It's absolutely delicious.

182
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:32,860
Honestly, we don't fuss
over food much in this house.

183
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:37,200
I'm always telling our housekeeper
to keep things simple and natural.

184
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,500
So for the most part,
we stick to fresh greens.

185
00:11:39,770 --> 00:11:42,110
It's pretty much a caveman diet, really.

186
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:45,140
That's the healthiest way to eat.

187
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:49,950
As a busy lawyer, you don't have time
to fuss over food anyway.

188
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:53,080
Thank you for being so understanding.

189
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:58,990
Now that
our kids have set their wedding date,

190
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:03,860
we should do this more often,
sharing meals and getting closer.

191
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:05,630
Let's become good friends.

192
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:09,330
I couldn't agree more.

193
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:13,340
- Please, have some of this.
- I'm going to gain weight at this rate.

194
00:12:14,740 --> 00:12:16,770
- Nonsense.
- Yes.

195
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,150
Mrs. Yeom.

196
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:30,320
Where are you off to so late?

197
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:33,490
I'm going to get something
to boost your energy, honey.

198
00:12:33,890 --> 00:12:35,630
You mean that side dish shop?

199
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:39,400
Yes, of course.

200
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:41,870
Have Mr. Kim take you.

201
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:45,940
You're really the only one
who looks out for me, honey.

202
00:12:58,250 --> 00:13:00,080
- Thank you.
- Enjoy your meal.

203
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:03,220
(Bomdama)

204
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,920
Baek Ho isn't even picking up his phone.

205
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:10,160
When Jang Mi makes up her mind,
she's frighteningly determined.

206
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:13,230
Calm down. Baek Ho isn't a kid.
He's a lawyer.

207
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:15,230
He's one of the smartest and sharpest
people I know.

208
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:17,430
What does being smart have to do with it?

209
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,740
Love makes fools of us all.

210
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:23,940
I'm worried sick something will happen
to one of them.

211
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:26,380
Then why don't you go home?
She might have gone there.

212
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:27,650
You think so?

213
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:30,050
- Tae Sook, I'm heading out.
- Okay.

214
00:13:30,110 --> 00:13:31,120
Right! My jacket.

215
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,250
We're here.

216
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,240
What are you doing here?

217
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:32,410
I'm not ready for any of this.

218
00:14:34,350 --> 00:14:35,610
How could you do this to me?

219
00:14:36,450 --> 00:14:37,720
- I...
- Baek Ho.

220
00:14:38,050 --> 00:14:39,050
That's enough.

221
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:42,020
You know how pathetic you look right now,
don't you?

222
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:43,220
Stay out of this, Jun Ho.

223
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,560
Just give me some time.

224
00:14:54,530 --> 00:14:56,770
Don't just blindside me
with a decision like this.

225
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,300
There's nothing more to say.

226
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,240
Goodness, you startled me!

227
00:15:02,570 --> 00:15:04,070
What's everyone doing out here
in front of the gate?

228
00:15:06,010 --> 00:15:07,110
You should head inside.

229
00:15:07,310 --> 00:15:09,580
You must be tired after your date.

230
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:15,220
I'll call you.

231
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:23,590
(Ma Dae Chang)

232
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:27,930
(Ma Dae Chang)

233
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,110
I'm so sorry, Baek Ho.

234
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:47,120
I'm so sorry.

235
00:15:52,990 --> 00:15:56,530
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

236
00:16:03,530 --> 00:16:04,700
Hey.

237
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,070
You just got out of the hospital.

238
00:16:07,570 --> 00:16:09,410
- Stop drinking.
- Tae Pyung.

239
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:14,680
This is all a nightmare, right?

240
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:18,250
None of this feels real.

241
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:23,120
I know how much you love Jang Mi.

242
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:27,060
But if you really love her,

243
00:16:27,620 --> 00:16:29,560
shouldn't you understand she has to leave?

244
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:31,130
Isn't that what love is?

245
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:36,270
Showing her you can move on and be okay
is another form of love.

246
00:16:36,330 --> 00:16:37,400
Jang Mi...

247
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:40,270
only made that choice because of me.

248
00:16:41,610 --> 00:16:42,940
If I hadn't let CEO Chae...

249
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:45,610
do that to me...

250
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,180
If we had just...

251
00:16:49,210 --> 00:16:50,610
gotten our revenge sooner,

252
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:53,780
this never would have happened.

253
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:55,050
That's not it.

254
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:58,720
If CEO Chae had never stolen
one of the twins in the first place...

255
00:16:59,690 --> 00:17:03,390
If she hadn't caused our father's death,
then none of this would have happened.

256
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,360
Let's get the story straight.

257
00:17:15,010 --> 00:17:17,940
The person you're calling is unavailable.
Connecting to voicemail...

258
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:22,110
Shin Ae Ran.

259
00:17:22,610 --> 00:17:25,480
Please, we need to talk.
Just answer the phone.

260
00:17:25,850 --> 00:17:29,150
So you're saying no women were transported
by a private ambulance?

261
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:32,290
Okay, got it.

262
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:36,790
(Clarion General Hospital)

263
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,530
I already called
the private ambulance association.

264
00:17:42,630 --> 00:17:44,570
Give it a rest. We've done all we can.

265
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:48,170
No. If I can just find Seo Rin,
Jang Mi will come back to me.

266
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:50,040
Look, I hate to be the one to say this,

267
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:52,540
but Jang Mi is someone who blames herself
for her mom getting hurt...

268
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,610
and for losing her father.

269
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:57,650
She couldn't bear the thought
of losing you, too.

270
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:01,750
And on top of that,
Chae Hwa Young is holding Seo Rin hostage.

271
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:04,590
That's why I have to find Seo Rin!

272
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,520
I know that,
and that's why I'm doing all this!

273
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:10,160
Tae Pyung, please just help me.

274
00:18:10,730 --> 00:18:11,730
Please?

275
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:17,730
Hey.

276
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:21,170
You really think CEO Chae is in love
with a piece of trash like you?

277
00:18:23,410 --> 00:18:24,580
He said what?

278
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,610
Manager Lee actually said that to you?

279
00:18:27,380 --> 00:18:28,380
Yes.

280
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:32,280
Are you really in love with Manager Lee?

281
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:35,550
For him to go so far
as to say that to me...

282
00:18:36,690 --> 00:18:39,160
means there is some truth to it.

283
00:18:39,490 --> 00:18:41,560
- Nam Bong.
- Just tell me the truth.

284
00:18:42,090 --> 00:18:43,960
- With Manager Lee...
- Please.

285
00:18:44,330 --> 00:18:46,130
How could you say something so absurd?

286
00:18:48,230 --> 00:18:49,230
Fine.

287
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:50,870
If you must know,

288
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:54,040
Manager Lee has had
a one-sided crush on me.

289
00:18:54,970 --> 00:18:56,170
A one-sided crush?

290
00:18:57,010 --> 00:18:58,040
Unbelievable.

291
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:01,550
I got the sense that
he had feelings for me.

292
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:03,550
Is that...

293
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:05,350
really true?

294
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:08,820
I'm so mortified.
I was hoping no one would ever find out.

295
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:11,120
Nam Bong.

296
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:13,760
I'm sure that made you very uncomfortable.

297
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:15,960
I should fire Manager Lee immediately.

298
00:19:16,890 --> 00:19:19,060
The nerve of him,
how dare he set his sights on me?

299
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,370
He must have seen how close we were...

300
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:25,340
and spouted all that nonsense
out of jealousy.

301
00:19:25,700 --> 00:19:27,170
Please let me apologize on his behalf.

302
00:19:31,740 --> 00:19:34,410
It's a beautiful day. Let's go on a trip.

303
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:37,310
With everything
that's been going on lately,

304
00:19:37,610 --> 00:19:40,920
I feel terrible that
we haven't had a proper date.

305
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:46,720
So where should we go?

306
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:49,290
When should we go, Nam Bong?

307
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:54,460
I want to spend the whole day
with just you.

308
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,140
Goodness.

309
00:20:07,210 --> 00:20:10,280
He's always catching a cold
now that he's getting older.

310
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:13,850
Who else is going to take care of him
but me?

311
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:18,320
My goodness, what happened here?

312
00:20:18,890 --> 00:20:20,990
It just happened.

313
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:23,590
Goodness.

314
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:27,730
Tae Pyung, you must've been so upset.

315
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:30,900
You're an ugly lady.

316
00:20:31,770 --> 00:20:33,000
You look like a twisted donut.

317
00:20:33,770 --> 00:20:34,770
Excuse me?

318
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:39,980
Suk Hee, was it?

319
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,650
I see Tae Pyung's mom...

320
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:46,080
has a habit of saying
the opposite of what she means.

321
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,650
Suk Hee doesn't lie.

322
00:20:50,650 --> 00:20:54,830
Ugly lady, you're flirting with Tae Pyung.

323
00:20:56,060 --> 00:20:57,360
Stop hitting on him.

324
00:20:57,660 --> 00:20:58,660
Goodness.

325
00:20:59,260 --> 00:21:00,430
Unbelievable.

326
00:21:00,730 --> 00:21:02,500
When was I ever flirting with him?

327
00:21:07,670 --> 00:21:09,840
Do you really think Jang Mi loves you?

328
00:21:10,340 --> 00:21:13,040
If you think she's marrying you for love,
you're dead wrong.

329
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:15,680
Do you think love is the only reason
to get married?

330
00:21:16,550 --> 00:21:19,180
I told you, love isn't everything.

331
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:21,550
Have you even thought about
where a loveless marriage ends up?

332
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:23,150
It's obvious.

333
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:25,860
You'll both be miserable and break up
because you can't stand it.

334
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:27,990
Stop trying to define my marriage for me.

335
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:31,330
- Couldn't you at least be happy for me?
- Happy for you?

336
00:21:31,630 --> 00:21:33,000
Did you just say be happy for you?

337
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:37,030
- Jang Mi is in love with me.
- Feelings change. Don't you know that?

338
00:21:37,730 --> 00:21:39,370
You think her feelings for you
will last forever?

339
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:41,070
I'm going to change...

340
00:21:41,570 --> 00:21:43,240
Jang Mi's heart to love me.

341
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:45,980
So stop messing with
your future sister-in-law.

342
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:47,280
There's no way she's marrying you.

343
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:50,710
- I won't let that happen.
- It doesn't matter if you object.

344
00:21:51,250 --> 00:21:53,680
This wedding isn't getting called off
just because you disapprove.

345
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:56,750
You have no right to stand
in the way of this marriage.

346
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:59,520
You think your disapproval will stop me
from getting married?

347
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,130
What is all this about?

348
00:22:07,230 --> 00:22:09,200
Baek Ho, don't tell me you're against
your brother's wedding too.

349
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:11,330
That's right. I'm against this marriage.

350
00:22:11,330 --> 00:22:13,270
Kang Baek Ho, shut up.

351
00:22:13,340 --> 00:22:16,040
First, your father was against it,
and now you?

352
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:19,110
Are you that upset about your brother
marrying into a wealthy family?

353
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:23,010
What's gotten into you two?
First, your father, and now you.

354
00:22:23,510 --> 00:22:25,080
I just don't understand it.

355
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:26,450
Let me say this again.

356
00:22:27,080 --> 00:22:28,550
I won't tolerate your disrespect.

357
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:30,250
Got it?

358
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:34,760
Jun Ho!

359
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:39,630
Baek Ho, not you too. What's wrong?

360
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:41,430
Is there some kind of problem...

361
00:22:41,870 --> 00:22:43,270
with Director Ma?

362
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:04,150
Dad, I hear you're against my marriage.

363
00:23:04,860 --> 00:23:06,020
Why is that?

364
00:23:08,490 --> 00:23:10,530
Please give me a reason I can accept.

365
00:23:12,060 --> 00:23:13,060
All right.

366
00:23:13,560 --> 00:23:16,700
This is just a hunch,
but regarding my car accident,

367
00:23:16,930 --> 00:23:19,600
I have a feeling CEO Chae was involved.

368
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:25,910
I can't go into details,
but the whole thing just feels wrong.

369
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:28,950
I need to sort things out
with CEO Chae first.

370
00:23:29,150 --> 00:23:33,320
So don't rush into this marriage.
Take your time and think it over.

371
00:23:33,650 --> 00:23:36,350
But CEO Chae was found innocent.

372
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:37,720
The real culprit even turned himself in.

373
00:23:37,790 --> 00:23:39,220
So why are you bringing this up now?

374
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:43,330
I told you.
Wait until I settle things with CEO Chae.

375
00:23:43,530 --> 00:23:45,560
Seriously, what has gotten into him?

376
00:23:50,530 --> 00:23:53,640
Honey, what is there
to settle with CEO Chae?

377
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:55,670
I just don't understand you, Dad.

378
00:23:55,870 --> 00:23:57,510
Do you hate seeing me succeed that much?

379
00:23:57,970 --> 00:24:00,410
If you want to ruin your son's future,

380
00:24:00,410 --> 00:24:01,550
then go right ahead.

381
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:08,390
Jun Ho.

382
00:24:13,860 --> 00:24:16,230
You raise your kids, and for what?

383
00:24:16,490 --> 00:24:18,760
He only ever thinks about himself.

384
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:25,800
Jang Mi.

385
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:30,940
What do you think of this dress?

386
00:24:36,910 --> 00:24:38,720
I actually like this one.

387
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:40,920
But that's not really your style, is it?

388
00:24:41,180 --> 00:24:43,920
Why? Are you upset because I'm picking
based on Seo Rin's taste?

389
00:24:44,890 --> 00:24:47,820
- That's not what I meant...
- Whether I'm Oh Jang Mi or Ma Seo Rin,

390
00:24:48,230 --> 00:24:51,060
you just want to marry me, don't you?

391
00:24:52,130 --> 00:24:53,530
So stay out of it.

392
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:14,380
What do you think, ma'am? Do you like it?

393
00:25:19,260 --> 00:25:22,130
This is awful. Why did you only bring me
such tacky dresses?

394
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:24,690
You still haven't picked one?

395
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:26,800
I don't like any of them.

396
00:25:27,060 --> 00:25:29,500
I could try on 100 more
and still wouldn't like any of them.

397
00:25:29,800 --> 00:25:31,170
Then let me pick one for you.

398
00:25:35,010 --> 00:25:38,110
Have Seo Rin try this one,
and for General Manager Kang...

399
00:25:39,210 --> 00:25:41,580
Do you have a tuxedo
that's a little more eye-catching?

400
00:25:41,710 --> 00:25:43,450
Excuse me? For the groom, not the bride?

401
00:25:43,450 --> 00:25:44,610
Yes.

402
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:47,550
They're the "dream couple"
of the Dream Hotel, aren't they?

403
00:25:47,950 --> 00:25:50,650
Seo Rin already turns heads
no matter what she wears,

404
00:25:52,020 --> 00:25:55,360
so shouldn't the groom, making his debut,
be the main attraction?

405
00:25:55,990 --> 00:25:57,460
Make sure it's something special.

406
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:58,900
Yes, of course.

407
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,440
We're getting married.

408
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:15,850
We'll be handing out
the invitations in person soon.

409
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:27,120
Hwa Young.

410
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:29,830
Professor Kang? What brings you here?

411
00:26:30,760 --> 00:26:33,200
- I'll take care of this, ma'am.
- Manager Lee.

412
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:34,660
I told you not to cross the line.

413
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:37,300
Know your place and get out.

414
00:26:45,010 --> 00:26:46,840
I was going to fire Manager Lee,

415
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:48,850
but he still has work to finish up.

416
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:52,980
Hwa Young,

417
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:57,650
I've been thinking
about this over and over.

418
00:26:58,890 --> 00:27:00,860
Should I just keep believing you?

419
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:03,990
You say you love me,
but were you just using me?

420
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:08,930
Is there really something going on
between you and Manager Lee?

421
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:13,700
Professor Kang.
This is a place of business.

422
00:27:14,170 --> 00:27:15,170
No.

423
00:27:15,810 --> 00:27:17,840
I think I'm going crazy. No, I am crazy.

424
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:20,180
I'm the one who's lost his mind.

425
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:29,590
I don't care what anyone says.

426
00:27:30,020 --> 00:27:32,620
No matter how loudly my reason screams no,

427
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,390
I...

428
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,090
I can't fight it.

429
00:27:37,590 --> 00:27:38,700
My heart...

430
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:41,500
only runs to you, Hwa Young.

431
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,200
I've lost the battle with myself.

432
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:48,510
So please, Hwa Young, you have to help me.

433
00:27:51,410 --> 00:27:52,410
Professor Kang...

434
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:55,780
Should we just run away
somewhere together?

435
00:27:56,410 --> 00:27:57,650
I want to.

436
00:27:58,420 --> 00:28:02,090
I want to disappear to somewhere
in the world with you, Nam Bong.

437
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:04,550
Hwa Young.

438
00:28:06,060 --> 00:28:07,060
I love you.

439
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,160
I love you.

440
00:28:15,930 --> 00:28:16,930
I love you, too.

441
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:20,840
I love you, Nam Bong.

442
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:25,740
You're the first person
to ever make me feel like a real woman.

443
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:27,980
I love you more than anyone in the world.

444
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,850
(The First Man)

445
00:29:05,320 --> 00:29:08,420
How could you stab me in the back
like this?

446
00:29:08,620 --> 00:29:11,220
If you keep saying you love CEO Chae,

447
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:12,490
I'll make you pay.

448
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:15,660
I think it's best
if you call off this wedding.

449
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,890
I will make Chae Hwa Young
weep tears of blood.

450
00:29:18,260 --> 00:29:19,630
And now, to top it all off,

451
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:21,500
an affair?

452
00:29:21,930 --> 00:29:24,400
Kang Jun Ho is just a pawn in my revenge.

453
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:30,110
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
